data.description: This is a recently renovated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath, 2-car garage home that has been thoughtfully upgraded with new luxury vinyl flooring throughout, new water-saving landscaping in the front yard, a fresh coat of paint, and an easy-to-maintain backyard with a child’s playset and storage shed. The main level comprises a spacious front living room with vaulted ceilings, a family room with a comforting gas fireplace that opens to an inviting eat-in kitchen that opens to the backyard. The kitchen has undergone a modern transformation, boasting 42" cabinets, generous counter space, and stainless steel appliances. Moving to the upper level, you'll discover the master bedroom with its private en suite, which includes double vanities for added comfort and convenience. Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom are also situated on this floor. For added convenience, the laundry facilities are placed upstairs. The home also boasts the installation of a new and efficient furnace and air conditioning unit (2021), a new roof (2021), and the addition of stylish 6-panel doors. It's conveniently located within walking distance of shopping, parks, and schools. It is also conveniently located near the Antler Creek Golf Course, as well as Schriever and Peterson Space Force bases, the United States Air Force Academy, and Fort Carson! This is a tremendous opportunity to make this your new home, and you can rest assured you won't be disappointed!
